en_115850_0	The Forest Department states that the fire which broke out yesterday (1st) noon at the Puttalam – Karuwalagaswewa – Ipalogama forest reserve has been controlled.
en_115850_1	It is said that a land of more than 20 hectares has been destroyed by the fire.
en_115850_2	The police suspects that the fire was caused by the spreading of a fire lit for hunting purposes.
